html(lang='en', xmlns:th='http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml')
  head(th:replace='common/header :: common-header')/
  body
    div(th:replace='common/header :: navbar')/
    .container
      .row(style='margin-bottom: -100px;')
        .row
          .col-xs-8
            h2.section-headline
              span User Account
          .col-xs-4
            a(th:href='@{/}')
              img.img-responsive(src='/imgs/logo.png')
        hr(style='position: absolute; width:100%; height:6px; background-color: #333; z-index: -1; margin-top: -80px;')
        img.img-responsive(src='/imgs/wood.png', style='margin-top: -75px;')
      .row(style='margin-top: 120px;')
        .col-xs-9.col-xs-offset-3
          h3 Shopping
          hr
          h4.question Q: How do I place an order?
          p
            | A: First you need to set up an account, once that is created you are ready to place an order.
          h4.question Q: How do I set up an account? 
          p
            | A: Click on the login button in the upper right hand corner of the main page and then click on create an
            | account.
          h4.question Q: How long does it take to process and ship orders?
          p
            | A: Please allow 1 - 3 business days (Monday-Friday) for order processing regardless of the shipping
            | method chosen. Once shipped you should receive your order within 2 - 10 business days. Please note that
            | 2 day and Overnight services refer to business days (Monday - Friday).
          h4.question Q: Are all of the items guaranteed in stock?
          p
            | A: We try to update the website as often as possible to reflect out of stock conditions. However, the
            | ability to order an item does not guarantee that it will be in stock when your order is processed. You
            | will be notified if an order is not available.
          h4.question Q: Why can't I choose the size and color I want?
          p
            | A: If you are unable to select a specific size or color, it typically means that the item is out of
            | stock. Try checking back in 2 - 3 weeks to see if your size or color is available.
          h4.question
            | Q: I can't find a specific item on the website, are there items available that are not listed on the
            | website?
          p
            | A: The items that are currently shown on our website represent what is currently available to view
            | and order online. There is a wider selection of merchandise available at the UVM Bookstore and the
            | Catamount Store. Please visit our stores when you are in the Burlington area.
          h4.question Q: How can I check the status of my order?
          p
            | A: If you have registered for an account at the UVM Bookstore, click on "My Account" and login with your
            | email address and password. You can view the status of any orders that were made while you were signed
            | in. You can also contact us at 1.800.331.7305 with your name, order number, and a request for
            | status of your order. Our office hours are Monday - Friday 8am -4:30pm EST
          h4.question Q: How can I cancel or change my order?
          p
            | A: You can cancel your order or make a change to it by contacting us at 1.999.999.9999 as soon as
            | possible after your order is placed with your name, order number, and a request for cancellation or a
            | description of the requested change. Our office hours are Monday Friday 8am 4:30pm. We will do our best
            | to cancel or modify your order, but we will not be able to complete the cancellation if your order has
            | been processed or shipped.
          h3 Shipping 
          hr
          p
            | The UVM Bookstore is proud to offer you competitive shipping rates. All of our shipments are
            | professionally packed to ensure the safety of your items in route.
          h4.question Q: How much is the shipping charge on orders?
          p
            | A: The shipping charge depends on the total amount of the merchandise ordered as well as the shipping
            | method chosen. There are some items that incur additional charges such as diploma frames $19.99 for an
            | oversized box and maple syrup $1.00 for double-boxing. The rate for chairs and rockers is $35.00 for
            | shipments east of the Mississippi and $45.00 west of the Mississippi.
          h4.question Q. What is your shipping method?
          p
            | A: We ship UPS, FedEx or US mail .
          h4.question Q: When will I receive my order?
          p
            | A: On average, your order will be received in 7 - 10 working days. During August and January, delivery
            | time may take longer.
